  "description": "<i>Tank Beat</i> is a mission based, arcade style tank simulator game. The player must take on the role of guardsman-in-training Vill Vitt and take back his home country of  after being stranded with a squad of parade tanks originally not meant for war.<br><br>The player controls a variety of tanks by using the touch screen to draw waypoints to clear the 30 missions found in the single player story mode surrounding around Vill Vitt's training. The game features a variety of real and fictional tanks for the player to choose, each with their own gameplay style, such as tanks without a movable turret, which must stop to turn to face the enemy.<br><br>The game also features a skirmish mode where the player can re-play any unlocked story missions and aim for a high score. A multiplayer battle mode is also included which allows up to four players to play together.",
